WEBVTT

03:00.680 --> 03:02.382
You really believe if I let
a guy like this

03:02.482 --> 03:04.884
do whatever he wants,
he gets bored and vanishes?

03:04.984 --> 03:07.820
Rick, would you be interested
in proving me wrong?

03:07.887 --> 03:09.822
Yes!

03:09.889 --> 03:11.090
Ignore them for a week
and see what happens.
